   1  *###############################################################################
   2  *### GET version 12.0
   3  *###
   4  *### Updated by Fayas Malik and Maria OL
   5  *### Extensive updation of transport sector
   6  *### Eight ship types: Container, general cargo and bulk, liquid tanker, gaseous tanker, cargo short, ferry short, ferry long, other ship
   7  *### Four aircraft types: short distance, medium and long distance passenger aircraft,and freight aircraft
   8  *### Three truck types: LCV, MFT, HFT
   9  *### To DO:
  10  *### - The climate
  11  *### - Add truck type
  12  *### - Biomass categories
  13  *### - Agriculture feedstock-ammonia
  14  *### - Result excel sheet correction and simplification
  15  *### - equations for sensitivity assessment for varying range and other Parameters
  16  *### - Aviation technical details
  17  *### - Adding Sustainable aviation fuels
  18  *### - Add FCREEV
  19  *### - modify industrial feedstock e.g. iron and steel etc.
  20  *### - Carbon budget revisions and nuclear investment
  21  *###############################################################################
